reviewText: Shipped/rec'd timely. Gift for father in law who loved it!
Great quality video of the story of the P-51 Mustang. Would recommend this to any P-51 lover out there!
An excellent addition to your aviation library.
it is an ok documentary but not what I expected...it could have been a little better but anything with a P-51 IS ok....

A must for the aviation buff.
I bought this as a gift for a friend and P51 enthusiast.
The content is interesting an photos great. You'll want to watch over and over
